any artifacts were written or committed. I inspected the repository state, read 
the harness and archetype templates, and measured the current package shape and 
JSR publishability. The next step is to write the five required planning 
artifacts and commit them to the branch.
    
    ## Changes
    
    No source or artifact changes were committed in this session. The working 
tree remains clean except for the untracked run metadata directory 
`.llm/tmp/run/openhands/pr-34/`.
    
